{
  "stem": "17625.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 160.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no way out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was only a way out from-- from-- from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- but that's why when-- when I was-- when I went to-- to clean up the crematorium from-- from-- from the [? cipher ?] there, I saw them working to the [?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sonder. ?] And it was-- and at that time, they-- they read the [INAUDIBLE], you know the numbers, from-- from-- from the beginning, not from the end.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my name was-- was mentioned there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This-- this is how it is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After-- well, how did I survive?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't come to that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "While we left at 12 o'clock, we went out from Auschwitz, from Birkenau on the way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was farm, a [INAUDIBLE] farm in-- in the-- with what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where the straw is, where the [INAUDIBLE] is, you know I mean?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the barn to rest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the morning, they assembled us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- [INAUDIBLE] was out of Auschwitz, Rybnik.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rybnik.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was all the vicinity from Auschwitz and Chrzanow, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This-- this-- This is-- this is my home-- how my-- my home turf.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the morning, they assembled us, and the SS men there with bayonets, just to-- to test, you know, in the straw, to test and-- and took us on the march.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't take the whole-- who camp, it was maybe 20-- 20,000 or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But but whoever made it, marched, marched.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Whoever was behind, they didn't bother with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But then they-- they finished him off and they came a truck where they then put him up on top of it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I, I was walking with this Schlomo Dragon.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
